s, and helping authors navigate the complexities of the digital landscape.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: var(--accent-color); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\">Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Editing & Proofreading</h3>\n                <p>Meticulous editorial services to polish your manuscript.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Marketing & Promotion</h3>\n                <p>Strategic campaigns to boost your book's visibility.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Metadata Optimization</h3>\n                <p>Ensuring your book is discoverable by the right readers.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container hero\">\n        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n        <p>Ready to publish your next masterpiece? Contact us today for a consultation.</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem;\">info@indigodigitalpublishing.com</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Indigo Digital Publishing. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}